To build and install lgmon:

        ./autogen.sh --program-suffix=<Printer Model Name>
        make
        make install

To build and install lgmon with AUTOCONF

You can set the following <Printer Model Name>.
	pixus560i
	pixus860i
	pixus990i

Example for building the pixus560i lgmon with the new automake and autoconf:
        ./autogen.sh --program-suffix=pixus560i
        make
        make install

